## Completion Checklist

- [ ] Story ID is unique and follows STORY-NNN pattern
- [ ] epic-ref points to an existing epic
- [ ] User Story follows "As a / I want / So that" format
- [ ] Every AC uses Given/When/Then format and is independently testable
- [ ] acceptance-criteria-count matches actual number of ACs
- [ ] Points are assigned (Fibonacci: 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13)
- [ ] If points > 8, consider splitting the story
- [ ] All dependencies reference existing story IDs
